To add new workflows we need to create a new .yml files inside the .github/workflows directory.

To use multi-line commands use "|"

Always install the software inside the runner before executing software related commands

If there are many workflows since "on: push" would trigger all the workflows we can disable the specific workflow and run the required one alone.


we can execute shell script inside the runner too. for the shell scripts to run it should have an "+x" permission always add this to your shell script inside the workflow